The Sun - Rise & Fall
Privacy Policy for The Sun - Rise & Fall
Last updated: 2023-08-11
Team Lundsgard
("we," "us," or "our") operates the iOS app
The Sun - Rise & Fall
mobile application (the "Service").
This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use our Service.
By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
Information Collection and Use
We collect information regarding your current position (latitude and longitude) to provide you with the Service, specifically to calculate the sun and moon up and down times based on your current location.
Location Information
We may use and store information about your location if you give us permission to do so. We use this data to provide features of our Service.
We do not store your location information, and it is only used within the app to provide the specific functionality described above.
You can enable or disable location services when you use our Service at any time by way of your device's settings.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
By email: support@lundsgard.com
By visiting this page on our website: https://devops.vision
